e customer lifecycle, we\'ll give you our favorite tactics and strategies for increasing conversions at each step.\r\n</p>\r\n <p class=\"grey_text\"><b>3) The Critical Metrics for Each Stage of Your SaaS Business</b><br>A SaaS business grows through 3 predictable stages. Not only do you want to focus on different metrics at each stage, there are clear benchmarks that show you when you can move to the next stage.<p class=\"grey_text\">It\'s completely free and there\'s no catch. Simply tell us where you want your SaaS Marketing Bundle delivered and we\'ll start sending it to you.</p>	 \r\n</p>\r\n </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row_black_wrapper overflow_fix clearfix \">\r\n<div class=\"row_inner overflow_fix clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"bookdet\">\r\n<div class=\"bookleft\">\r\n<h1>Book name will be place here.</h1>\r\n<img src=\"http://demo.code5fixer.com/2013/rails/wp-content/themes/thecompellingimage/source/images/img_book.jpg\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bookright\">\r\n<span>Please submit your information and download the book.</span>\r\n<span class=\"big\">First Name</span><input type=\"text\">\r\n<span class=\"big\">Your Email</span><input type=\"text\">\r\n<span><input type=\"checkbox\">Yes! I want to receive all guides about book. </span><span><a>Send Your Information</a></span>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Whitepaper', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '61-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-08-16 18:26:31', '2013-08-16 18:26:31', '', '61', 'http://wordpress.com/rails/61-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0', '');
